{"tid":1938990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［最後9個工作日］區諾軒：仲有一個界別可衝關少人講：出版界！","createTime":"2020-03-23T01:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T08:24:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"654725904242c0d087fc8f169a296cf4d70c6f38","tid":1938990,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:53:43.000Z","msg":"唔好再等5月2號！5月2號係新登記，4月2號係轉界別，你本身有超區張票轉界別即係4月2號就截喇！<br />\n<br />\n最後一個界別可以衝關，就係出版界。之前擺較少注意力，有朋友提我要介紹下，我盡力用現有資料同大家講，唔好意思！<br />\n<br />\n* 我知道有另一種方法係走發行人條路。￼請參照：￼￼ <a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_14.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fblog-post_14.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=dfe3d7cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_14.html</a><br />\n甚至某程度上更容易，￼￼但我這裡只介紹註冊報刊。<br />\n<br />\n總之，你有<br />\n1) 有限公司登記，轉業務係出版（printing）、<br />\n2) 填好報刊註冊處表格、BR副本/ 身分證副本<br />\n3) 註冊費(首次註冊費用$1140)<br />\n4) 報刊樣本(承印人的姓名及地址 應登載於該報刊的頭版或最後一版), 留意<br />\n<br />\n郵寄方式 送交電影、報刊及物品管理辦事處。<br />\n<br />\n****搵區議員/區議員自己註冊份單張試下啦****<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/exportfrontier/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fexportfrontier%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=fb6951df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/exportfrontier/</a><br />\n<br />\n電影、報刊及物品管理辦事處<br />\n地址：香港灣仔告士打道5號稅務大樓39樓<br />\n辦公時間：星期一至五 上午8時45分至1時 及 下午2時至6時<br />\n電 話：報刊管理室：2594 5832 (馮燕婷女士)<br />\n<br />\n－－－－<br />\n🎥【Youtube 頻道】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/anhyoutube\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fanhyoutube&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=670c18af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/anhyoutube</a><br />\n📣【Telegram】<a href=\"http://t.me/aunokhin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faunokhin&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=43a381d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/aunokhin</a><br />\n🐦【Twitter】<a href=\"http://twitter.com/loktinau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Floktinau&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=00371515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/loktinau</a>"},{"pid":"beaa8b5fb90b7911c454d76b63429f8f5ef15f17","tid":1938990,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:54:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"12282bfd790da7fefa19b0560bebb1deb58bc2bd","tid":1938990,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:55:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"451105ae27b3380435793990f8cd24bd9d8df7b5","tid":1938990,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88e940bf542c7961de7a128a440820aef9da6c6","tid":1938990,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1d53f769554aaebd0b6c1fc34568ade114337b","tid":1938990,"uid":21817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:56:28.000Z","msg":"而家政府唔開工,會唔會變左唔幫你處理功能組別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edad71f3fccb2b78895435409c37e0c0ff81b147","tid":1938990,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:58:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c4ec638b8a890719f57f01bbfcc7277e5a327a8","tid":1938990,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:58:47.000Z","msg":"重點功能界別的whatapps Hotline<br />\n<br />\nGeneral whatapps Hotline : 65391922<br />\n體演文出whatapps Hotline : 66700860<br />\n進出口界whatapps Hotline : 68461562<br />\n飲食界whatapps Hotline : 9180 3949 / 66812202<br />\n批發及零售whatapps Hotline : 65391922<br />\n<br />\nGeneral FB Page: 功能組別和你解<br />\n進出口界FB Page: 進出口界600+<br />\n----<br />\n即Check:<br />\n功能組別指定協會<br />\n登記為功能組別選民資格<br />\n按 <a href=\"https://handyhands.com.hk/fbm.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhandyhands.com.hk%2Ffbm.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=3118a639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://handyhands.com.hk/fbm.html</a> 開啟Messenger就用到。<br />\n指定協會大整合：入會資格、價錢、介紹人、申請表。搵岩協會，即時加入。內附選民登記/更改表。<br />\n:fire:多你一票 多好多:fire:<br />\n上年光復區議會 今年光復埋功能組別 為下年選委選舉做準備<br />\n#手動傳 #只傳同路人<br />\n-----<br />\n中小企商界可以入嘅特首選委界別，佔159席，足以變天！<br />\n<br />\n開公司 (萬能界)<br />\n- 帶身份證去灣仔税局搞，俾$250，30分鐘搞掂 @businessfrontier<br />\n- 輕量級 &gt; 體育界 $2000/ 紡織界 $61/ 出版界 $1140 (撳個掣就得)<br />\n- 重量級 &gt; 商界 $3900/ 工業界 $2970/ 零售界 $1180/ 僱主聯合會 $4800<br />\n- 集中首選 &gt; 進出口界 $240+1320 (1年以上BR+商業地址）<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_98.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fblog-post_98.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=1f34a265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_98.html</a><br />\n<br />\n進出口界 (集中首選)(1年以上BR+商業地址）<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_99.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_99.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=df63c522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_99.html</a><br />\n<br />\n體育界 (撳個掣就得)<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_98.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fblog-post_98.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=1f34a265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_98.html</a><br />\n<br />\n紡織及製衣界 (史上最平)<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=1f80ea1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post.html</a><br />\n<br />\n商界 (第一)<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_56.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_56.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=95548611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_56.html</a><br />\n<br />\n工業界 (第一）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/businessfrontier/56\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbusinessfrontier%2F56&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=069138f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/businessfrontier/56</a><br />\n30個行業合資格： <a href=\"https://t.me/businessfrontier/161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbusinessfrontier%2F161&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=dfe8713d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/businessfrontier/161</a><br />\n<br />\n批發及零售界<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/02/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F02%2Fblog-post.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=55ae9ae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/02/blog-post.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港僱主聯合會<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_26.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_26.html&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=7